<BaseLayout
  title="About - Anastasia Bessonova"
  description="About Anastasia Bessonova - Narrative Designer for games and animation."
>
  <section class="card">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Anastasia Bessonova is a <strong>Porto-based narrative designer</strong> working across
      <strong>games and animation</strong>. Her focus is building story systems that support
      player agency, strong character voice, and clear production constraints.
    </p>

    <p>
      She works from early concept through to implementation-ready content - aligning narrative with
      design goals, pacing, and gameplay loops, and collaborating closely with design, art, and audio.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h2>What I do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Story and structure</strong> - loglines, beats, worldbuilding, character arcs</li>
      <li><strong>Interactive narrative</strong> - branching, conditions, variables, quest logic</li>
      <li><strong>Dialogue and voice</strong> - dialogue, barks, VO notes, localization-friendly writing</li>
      <li><strong>Implementation</strong> - engine tools, spreadsheets, narrative bibles, handoff docs</li>
      <li><strong>Iteration</strong> - playtest feedback, rewrites, polish passes</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

