      <li>Unity / Unreal (as needed)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section card">
    <h2>Now</h2>
    <p>
      Available for freelance and studio work - especially projects that value strong character writing,
      clear narrative structure, and tight collaboration with design.
